window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>***A Fake Relationship, Brother's Best Friend, Steamy Hockey Romance*** </p> <p><b>What’s worse than being in a fake relationship with my childhood crush? When he's a notorious NHL party-boy and my brother’s best friend!</b></p> <p>Being hired as the PR representative for the hockey team I’ve always been a fan of, should be a dream come true, especially because my old crush plays for them.</p> <p>My suggestion to save Briggs's career is solid… have him fake date someone wholesome who can change his image. That’s when my big mouth gets in the way and I admit to being the-girl-next-door.</p> <p>Now… my boss is offering me the promotion of a lifetime, but it comes with strings…</p> <p>Fake date Briggs Conley!</p> <p>Now I have to fix Briggs’ reputation, lie to our families, keep my MMA fighter brother from pummeling his best friend, and stop myself from falling further for my childhood crush, all while we're forced to live together and pretend to be madly in love in front of the cameras.</p> <p>What could possibly go wrong?</p> <p>How about when my brother ends up in our guest bedroom and I end up with a pro hockey player in my bed.</p>"; 
